message.body: Hey! What is your schedule tomorrow?
Hiii! So I'm in the jerz but will be back in silver spring around 3ish or 4....so I can be in frederick at 5ish at the earliest...what is your day looking like?
I will be free in the afternoon. I can get there by 5 too but we can meet up a little later so you're not stressed. Maybe around 6ish? And if its too much for you tell me!
Yes 6 is perfect! Christy was telling me there's a really good restaurant that's kind of a diner, it's owned by the guy who owns s place callef volt... I'll look it up!
Oo awesome! Yeah let's go there
Okay great! The address is 880 north east st, it's called family meal diner. I just made us a reservation on opentable. Yayy so excited to see you!!
Oh wow you're the best! I'm so excited :)
Hey! I'm going to be like 20 minutes late. I wanted to leave now but this recruit won't be here until 5:00.
Okay no worries! I made the reservation for 6:30 just in case, so we're good!
